<p>Of course, Mafia: The Old Country’s release window differs a bit when it comes to the rest of the world. </p><h2>Mafia: The Old Country Unlock Times</h2><p><strong>Tokyo (JST)</strong></p><p>Steam: August 8, 2 AM</p><p>Console: August 8, 12 AM</p><p><strong>London (BST)</strong></p><p>Steam: August 7, 5 PM</p><p>Console: August 8, 12 AM</p><p><strong>São Paulo (BRT)</strong></p><p>Steam: August 7, 1 PM</p><p>Console: August 8, 12 AM</p><p><strong>Sydney (AEST)</strong></p><p>Steam: August 8, 2 AM</p><p>Console: August 8, 12 AM</p><p><strong>Singapore (SGT)</strong></p><p>Steam: August 8, 12 AM</p><p>Console: August 8, 12 AM</p><p><strong>Auckland (NZST)</strong></p><p>Steam: August 8, 4 AM</p><p>Console: August 8, 12 AM</p><p><strong>Palermo (CEST)</strong></p><p>Steam: August 7, 6 PM</p><p>Console: August 8, 1 AM</p><p>As you can see, Mafia: The Old Country’s unlock times vary. Those looking to play sooner than later can opt to purchase it on a given platform. Regardless, everyone will be able to play the action-adventure prequel come sometime next week.</p>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
